TITLE

  envSOF21

VERSION

  2.1

AUTHOR

  Thomas Aglassinger <agi@sbox.tu-graz.ac.at>

DESCRIPTION

  **This project is archived and no longer maintained.**

  This is an Eiffel/Sofa add-on for GoldEd Studio 6. It consists of
  syntax parser, feature scanner, toolbar and a couple of ARexx
  scripts to interface with the Sofa distribution of the SmallEiffel
  compiler.

FEATURES

  Colorful, practical and free.

NEW FEATURES

  - The syntax parser now is a context parser supporting the
    "official" generic keyword settings.
  - Fixed some buttons in the "Eiffel (Short)" toolbar.

SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS

  - Sofa/SmallEiffel, available from http://www.owlnet.net/amiga/sofa/.

  - rexxdossupport.library, available from aminet:util/rexx/

  - GoldEd Studio 6, available from http://members.tripod.com/golded/.

AVAILABILITY

  aminet:text/edit/envSOF21.lha

PRICE

  Freeware.

DISTRIBUTABILITY

  Freely distributable as long no files are added or removed from the
  archive.

